obvious.data
Class DataFactory

java.lang.Object
  obvious.data.DataFactory
Direct Known Subclasses:
DataFactoryImpl
public abstract class DataFactory
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract Class DataFactory. A factory that can create Network and Table instances. Several methods are proposed to build such instances from existing instances of other tables or from Obvious Schema(s). Each binding of Obvious should implement this class.

Version:
$Revision$
Author:
Jean-Daniel Fekete
